designed by me in the year 1979.<br>
<br>
1. The ship has a mass of 300,000 kilograms.<br>
2. It has a mass ratio of 3/1.<br>
3. It has 200,000 kilograms of Loh stored in a <br>
40,000 titanium metal tank.<br>
4.It has two simple , 10 meter diameter ion engines.<br>
5. In these engines, there is a conical steel anode, <br>
and a ring shaped cathode made of steel.There are two<br>
aluminium screens whose holes are precisely aligned with<br>
each other.There is a .34 meter gap between those screens. The electric disharge ionizes the h2, Then the<br>
+ ions are accelerated in the electric field. Then they are expelled to generate thrust, and neutralized by electron emitters.The ion engines  have a casing of fiberglass around them. There two  -  negative electric fields on the two screens. Each ion  engine accelerates a  maximium mass of 1/2 gram of ions per second, and a minimium mass of 1/2000 of a gram of ions per second. <br>
On the first screen  there is a - 1000 Ev electric field.<br>
On the second screen there is a - 1,001,000 Ev electric<br>
field.<br>
<br>
6. The crew module has a mass of 30,000 kilograms.<br>
<br>
7. The nuclear fission powered electric generator has a mass of 30,000 kilograms, and A specific power A of<br>
100 to 1000 watts for each pound of its weight.<br>
<br>
 8. This nuclear reactor generates from 13.4 Mw to<br>
143 Mw of electric power. <br>
 <br>
9.At the peak power level there is more then  enough energy to accelerate one  gram of ions to 500 <br>
kilometers a second, or to accelerate 1 milligram of ions,<br>
to about 15000 kilometers a second.<br>
<br>
10. The specific impulse range is 50,000 to  1,500,000 <br>
 seconds for this ion drive. The thrust range is 3300<br>
pounds to 100 pounds.<br>
11. The acceleration range is .01 Gs to .0003 Gs<br>
for this ion drive vessel.<br>
12. By the rocket equation the maximium velocities<br>
attainable for this ion drive space ship is 550 km/sec <br>
to 16,500 km/sec. At highest Si it can get 100 km/sec<br>
in added velocity per year , at lowest si it can 3000<br>
km/sec in added velocity per year. In order to reach maximium delta v at highest Si 16 years of acceleration are required.This ship can cruise all the nine planets,<br>
and it can go at least .45 light years from the sun on a roundtrip within 16 years flight time.Questions comments et el?<br>
