Actually it will take 160 years not 16  years to<br>
 reach this ships maximium delta V. So actually<br>
the greatest distance it can go from the sun in 80<br>
years not 8 years is about 1.5 light years not .45<br>
light years. In eight years however  it can reach only about 800 km/sec not 8000 km/sec. In eight years it can go just about 64,000,000,000 miles from the sun at maximium  Si. At the lowest Si it can go  about 55,000,000,000 miles from the sun in eight years.<br>
The origional mission of this ship was to carry out a manned fly by of the Planets Mars , Jupiter, Saturn,<br>
Uranus, Neptune, And Pluto. .Then it was intended<br>
to  actually leave the solar system while carrying a<br>
human crew , travel to a piont 64,000,000,000 miles from the sun, shut down the ion drive: turn around<br>
